50|$|The Nariño <b>massacres</b> (Masacres en Nariño) {{were two}} <b>massacres</b> of {{indigenous}} Awá {{people in the}} Nariño Department of Colombia perpetrated {{by members of the}} rebel Revolutionary Armed Forces of Colombia (FARC) in February 2009. A total of 27 Awás were <b>massacred,</b> including women and young children.|$|R
